11. Points to Mention in Interview
----------------------------------

✓ Hash Table based container.
✓ Stores duplicate values.
✓ No ordering.
✓ Average O(1) operations.
✓ erase(value) removes ALL occurrences.
✓ erase(iterator) removes only ONE occurrence.
✓ count() returns duplicate count.
